E%26quot%3BHe%20had%20started%20as%20a%20dishwasher%20and%2C%20by%20the%20end%2C%20he%20was%20a%20manager%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20recent%20grad%20didn't%20have%20tech%20experience%2C%20to%20Weaver%2C%20he'd%20shown%20longevity%20with%20a%20company%20and%20a%20desire%20to%20take%20on%20more%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20definitely%20worth%20a%20conversation%2C%26quot%3B%20Weaver%20said.%20The%20man%20eventually%20got%20the%20job%20and%20has%20since%20been%20promoted%20multiple%20times%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20kind%20of%20feel-good%20story%20that%20seems%20impossible%20to%20repeat%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-hard-to-find-job-us-though-unemployment-low-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejob%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20can%20unfold%20like%20an%20obstacle%20course%20%E2%80%94%20one%20where%20the%20obstacles%20are%20the%20technologies%20that%20many%20companies%20use%20to%20filter%C2%A0and%20reject%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20for%20all%20the%20fear%20of%20so-called%20applicant-tracking%20systems%2C%20often%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20bot%20that's%20doing%20the%20booting%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20still%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'The%20ATS%20doesn't%20care'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMark%20Jensen%2C%20a%20recruiter%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fupswingtalent.ca%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUpswing%20Talent%20Acquisition%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20job%20seekers%20often%20focus%20too%20much%20on%20sneaking%20past%20an%20ATS%20to%20get%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20all%20think%20that%20the%20applicant-tracking%20system%20is%20some%20magical%20technology%20that%20screens%20people%20out%20on%20its%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20ATS%20doesn't%20care.%20It's%20just%20a%20repository.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20recruiters%20often%