%2Fjob-applications-hiring-ai-bots-spam-resume-cover-letter-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emake%20you%20a%20serial%20applier%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%203%25%20ROI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20even%20though%20it's%20easier%20than%20ever%20to%20apply%20for%20jobs%2C%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20you%20should%20go%20wild.%20Applying%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsimple-cover-letter-example-unemployed-job-search-never-hear-back-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20more%20than%201%2C000%20roles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20example%2C%20doesn't%20guarantee%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAaron%20Cleavinger%2C%20a%20managing%20partner%20at%20Murdoch%20Mason%20Executive%20Search%20Group%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20his%20firm's%20research%20shows%20that%20when%20applicants%20apply%20for%20positions%2C%20that%20effort%20turns%20into%20%26quot%3Bmeaningful%20conversations%26quot%3B%20only%20about%203%25%20of%20the%20time.%20He%20said%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20people%20shouldn't%20go%20for%20jobs%2C%20but%20they%20likely%20need%20to%20limit%20how%20often%20they%20focus%20on%20clicking%20that%20submit%20button.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20it's%203%25%20value%2C%20perhaps%20you%20should%20only%20spend%203%25%20of%20your%20time%20doing%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20else%20should%20job%20seekers%20do%3F%20Cleavinger%20said%20it's%20about%20constantly%20challenging%20yourself%20to%20appear%20different%20from%20other%20candidates%20who%20are%20equally%20or%20more%20qualified%20than%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20do%20you%20stand%20out%20so%20that%20when%20there's%20a%20big%20pile%20of%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20or%20a%20giant%20list%20of%20LinkedIn%20profiles%20to%20look%20through%20that%20you'd%20be%20the%20one%20to%20come%20on%20top%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJensen%2C%20the%20recruiter%20with%20Upswing%20Talent%20Acquisition%2C%20said%20the%20power%20also%20rests%20with%20those%20doing%20the%20hiring%20to%20make%20wise%20decisions%20about%20how%20to%20use%20an%20ATS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20recruiter%20and%20how%20they%20choose%20to%20filter%20to%20make%20hopefully%20the%20most%20relevant%20candidates%20bubble%20up%20to%20the%20top%2C%20so%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20review%20all%20400%20or%201%2C000%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-your-resume-gets-rejected-job-search-bots-people-ats-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714816321000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6635359310dfcda40966b09d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-your-resume-gets-rejected-job-search-bots-people-ats-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Job%20seekers%20often%20fear%20applicant-tracking%20systems%2C%20but%20a%20big%20reason%20why%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20gets%20rejected%20might%20not%20be%20technology%2C%20but%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tparadis%40businessinsider.com%20(Tim%20Paradis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-your-resume-gets-rejected-job-search-bots-people-ats-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Taiwan%2C%20US%20hold%20trade%20talks%20in%20Taipei%20for%20agricultural%20products%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714815928000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109838123%2Cimgsize-310221.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftaiwan-us-hold-trade-talks-in-taipei-for-agricultural-products%2Farticleshow%2F109837849.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109837849.cms%5C%22%2