20drone%20for%20an%20operation%20near%20the%20town%20of%20Chasiv%20Yar%2C%20Donetsk%20region%2C%20on%20April%2022%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663508dd10dfcda409668864%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221293%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Ukrainian%20soldier%20from%20the%20battalion%20of%20unmanned%20attack%20air%20systems%20%26quot%3BAchilles%26quot%3B%20of%20the%2092nd%20Separate%20Assault%20Brigade%20prepares%20the%20%26quot%3BVampir%26quot%3B%20night%20drone%20for%20an%20operation%20near%20the%20town%20of%20Chasiv%20Yar%2C%20Donetsk%20region%2C%20on%20April%2022%2C%202024.%3Cp%3EAnatolii%20Stepanov%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDrone%20warfare%20is%20changing%20fast%20and%20demands%20battalions%20of%20specialists%20to%20fully%20exploit%20its%20potential.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20group%20would%20fly%20support%20drones%20to%20increase%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20its%20attack%20and%20spy%20drones.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20air%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20has%20become%20a%20cat-and-mouse%20game%20where%20drones%20must%20constantly%20evolve.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EExperience%20in%20Ukraine%20suggests%20that%20armies%20should%20concentrate%20drones%20in%20special%20battalions%20that%20have%20the%20skills%20pilots%20to%20fly%20them%20and%20the%20programmers%20to%20rapidly%20adapt%20to%20constant%20jamming%2C%20according%20to%20British%20defense%20experts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUkrainian%20data%20shows%20%26quot%3Bthe%20efficiency%20of%20%5BUnmanned%20Aerial%20Vehicle%5D%20operations%20when%20conducted%20by%20a%20dedicated%20formation%20has%20risen%20from%2010%20percent%20up%20to%2070%20percent%20for%20some%20mission%20sets%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rusi.org%2Fexplore-our-research%2Fpublications%2Foccasional-papers%2Fmass-precision-strike-designing-uav-complexes-land-forces%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20Royal%20United%20Services%20Institute%2C%20a%20British%20think%20tank.%20The%20report%20did%20not%20provide%20any%20more%20specifics%20on%20the%20data%2C%20other%20than%20a%20footnote%20that%20said%20it%20was%20based%20on%20Ukrainian%20General%20Staff%20%26quot%3Bdatasets%20of%20mission%20performance%20between%20different%20formations%26quot%3B%20that%20RUSI%20accessed%20in%20Ukraine%20in%20February%202024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20RUSI%20report%20advocates%20the%20creation%20of%20%26quot%3Bmass%20precision%20strike%20complex%26quot%3B%20units%20that%20launch%20integrated%20swarms%20of%20drones%20comprised%20of%20different%20types%20of%20reconnaissance%20and%20combat%20UAVs.%20The%20concept%20seems%20similar%20to%20%26quot%3Bstrike%20packages%26quot%3B%20of%20manned%20combat%20jets%2C%20which%20combine%20attack%2C%20escort%20and%20electronic%20warfare%20planes%20on%20a%20mission.%20To%20be%20clear%2C%20the%20report%20isn't%20calling%20for%20infantry%20platoons%20to%20be%20stripped%20of%20their%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-us-marine-kamikaze-drones-going-to-ukraine-are-powerful-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebackpack-carried%20drones%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20have%20proven%20indispensable%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20Middle%20East.%20But%20it%20does%20argue%20that%20for%20some%20tasks%2C%20such%20as%20long-range%20surveillance%20and%20strike%2C%20it's%20more%20efficient%20and%20economical%20to%20achieve%20this%20through%20dedicated%20units.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BUAVs%20may%20be%20distributed%20to%20provide%20units%20with%20situational%20awareness%2C%20but%20mass%20precision%20strike%20should%20be%20managed%20by%20a%20specialist%20formation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20concluded.%20In%20addition%20to%20better%20mission%20planning%20by%20personnel%20trained%20and%20experienced%20in%20drone%20operations%2C%20%26quot%3Bexperience%20from%20contemporary%20theatres%20shows%20that%20almost%20all%20UAV%20capabilities%20are%20highly%20susceptible%20to%20hard%20counters%20as%20the%20adversary%20learns%20how%20the%20UAV%20functions%3B%20capabilities%20must%20therefore%20be%20continuously%20adapted%20and%20their%20supporting%20mission%20data%20files%20updated.%20This%20requires%20scarce%20skills%20such%20as%20UAV%20design%20and%20programming%20and%20the%20accumulation%20of%20data%20centrally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERUSI%20envisions%20each%20drone%20battalion%20being%20equipped%20with%20everything%20needed%20to%20conduct%20a%20variety%20of%20UAV%20operations.%20The%20units%20would%20comprise%20%26quot%3Bairframes%20and%20their%20payloads%2C%20and%20the%20launch%20crews%2C%20command%20links%2C%20planning%20tools%2C%20intelligence%20support%20and%20design%20teams%20required%20to%20field%20the%20capability%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20RUSI%20researchers%20Jack%20Watling%20and%20Justin%20Bronk.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDrone%20battalions%20would%20have%20five%20types%20of%20UAVs%20whose%20capabilities%20range%20from%20spying%20enemy%20advances%20to%20blasting%20critical%20rear%20sites%20with%20explosives.%20This%20would%20include%20%26quot%3Bsituational%20awareness%20UAVs%20optimized%20for%20tactical%20reconnaissance%3B%20tactical%20strike%20UAVs%3B%20ISR%20%5Breconnaissance%5D%20UAVs%20able%20to%20penetrate%20into%20operational%20depth%3B%20operational%20strike%20UAVs%3B%20and%20platform-launched%20effects%20designed%20specifically%20to%20synchronize%20with%20and%20enable%20other%20weapons%20systems.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20idea%20is%20to%20have%20self-contained%20formations%20that%20can%20identify%20and%20destroy%20targets%20across%20the%20battlefield%20and%20beyond.%20To%20support%20friendly%20ground%20troops%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20enemy%2C%20flocks%20of%20expendable%20reconnaissance%20drones%20would%20operate%20up%20to%205%20miles%20beyond%20the%20enemy%20front%20line.%20They%20would%20locate%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famid-ukraine-war-us-army-seeking-new-tank-killing-drone-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etargets%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20such%20as%20armored%20vehicles%20and%20infantry%20trenches%2C%20that%20could%20be%20quickly%20hit%20by%20the%20battalion's%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-war-top-tanks-taken-out-by-cheap-hobby-drones-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Echeap%20attack%20drones%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20longer-range%20reconnaissance%20drones%20would%20stalk%20up%20to%2060%20miles%20into%20the%20enemy's%20rear%2C%20searching%20for%20artillery%20pieces%2C%20air%20defense%20batteries%20and%20command%20posts%20that%20could%20be%20hit%20by%20missiles%20and%20other%20guided%20weapons.%20The%20drone%20battalion%20would%20also%20launch%20long-range%20strike%20weapons%20%E2%80%94%20with%20a%20range%20out%20to%20300%20miles%20%E2%80%94%20that%20could%20destroy%20fixed%20sites%2C%20such%20as%20supply%20depots%2C%20bridges%20and%20ammunition%20dumps.%20%26quot%3BBy%20offering%20a%20persistent%20threat%20of%20precision%20strike%20against%20logistical%20infrastructure%20and%20command%20and%20control%20elements%2C%20these%20capabilities%20would%20add%20significant%20friction%20to%20the%20enemy's%20ability%20to%20resupply%20and%20coordinate%20forces%2C%20and%20therefore%20to%20achieve%20concentration%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%20%26quot%3BThese%20capabilities%20also%20represent%20a%20concern%20for%20air%20and%20naval%20forces%20insofar%20as%20they%20threaten%20infrastructure%20and%20basing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ukraine%20drone%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651d49e92ce014759e74522e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Ukrainian%20serviceman%20launches%20a%20drone%20during%20a%20press%20tour%20in%20the%20Zhytomyr%20Region%2C%20northern%20Ukraine%20on%20September%2020%2C%202023.%20%3Cp%3EKirill%20Chubotin%20%2F%20Ukrinform%2FFuture%20Publishing%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20maximize%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20reconnaissance%20and%20strike%20drones%20%E2%80%94%20and%20to%20keep%20them%20from%20being%20knocked%20down%20by%20enemy%20air%20defenses%20%E2%80%94%20the%20battalion%20would%20also%20have%20a%20variety%20of%20support%20UAVs.%20This%20would%20include%20long-endurance%20airborne%20communications%20drones%20to%20relay%20datalinks%20between%20the%20combat%20UAVs%20and%20ground%20operations%2C%20electronic%20warfare%20drones%20to%20jam%20radars%20and%20communications%20systems%2C%20and%20decoy%20drones%20to%20confuse%20enemy%20air%20defenses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Ukraine%20conflict%20demonstrates%20how%20warfare%20has%20become%20a%20cat-and-mouse%20game%20where%20drones%20must%20constantly%20evolve%20to%20survive%20enemy%20jamming%20of%20their%20control%20links.%20%26quot%3BAs%20of%20mid-2023%2C%20the%20average%20period%20of%20peak%20effectiveness%20for%20a%20newly%20deployed%20UAV%20navigation%20and%2F%20or%20control%20system%20on%20the%20battlefield%20was%20around%20two%20weeks%2C%20with%20degrading%20effectiveness%20over%20four%20more%20weeks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20noted.%20%26quot%3BBetween%20six%20and%2012%20weeks%2C%20the%20adversary%20would%20have%20gathered%20sufficient%20data%20on%20the%20waveforms%20and%20techniques%20being%20used%20to%20start%20effectively%20jamming%20and%2For%20spoofing%20the%20system%20across%20the%20front.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENon-drone%20units%20lack%20the%20capability%20to%20identify%20and%20develop%20the%20software%20and%20communications%20challenges%20to%20respond%20to%20enemy%20countermeasures.%20%26quot%3BIt%20therefore%20makes%20sense%20to%20concentrate%20UAV%20operation%20if%20UAVs%20are%20parts%20of%20a%20mass%20precision%20strike%20complex%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20concluded.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20issue%20of%20whether%20to%20concentrate%20or%20disperse%20assets%20is%20an%20old%20one.%20Until%20World%20War%20II%2C%20tanks%20were%20dispersed%20in%20small%20packets%20among%20infantry%20divisions%2C%20while%20aircraft%20were%20assigned%20to%20the%20ground%20forces.%20But%20experience%20proved%20that%20tanks%20were%20most%20effective%20when%20massed%20in%20tank%20divisions%2C%20and%20aircraft%20were%20best%20assigned%20to%20an%20independent%20air%20force%20that%20specialized%20in%20aerial%20operations%20(some%20still%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D1717df10855529f8276cc8af6ed08ac535f5c82b0c7ef140ed76bf7c411d64ac%26postID%3D663506bb2c3267408d063313%26postSlug%3Darmies-need-their-own-drone-air-force-flown-by-specialists-study-says-2024-5%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FGrounded-Abolishing-Studies-Conflict-Diplomacy%252Fdp%252F0813165571%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Equestion%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20wisdom%20of%20the%20latter).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDrone%20operations%20may%20very%20well%20be%20more%20efficient%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20specialized%20battalions.%20But%20regular%20units%20will%20inevitably%20want%20their%20own%20drones%20that%20are%20available%20when%20needed%2C%20rather%20than%20having%20to%20request%20support%20from%20others.%20The%20issue%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20settled%20quickly%20or%20easily.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EMichael%20Peck%20is%20a%20defense%20writer%20whose%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Forbes%2C%20Defense%20News%2C%20Foreign%20Policy%20magazine%2C%20and%20other%20publications.%20He%20holds%20an%20MA%20in%20political%20science%20from%20Rutgers%20Univ.%20Follow%20him%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2F%40mipeck1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ETwitter%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fmipeck%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ELinkedIn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farmies-need-their-own-drone-air-force-flown-by-specialists-study-says-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714813201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66350a520dfb1341e9026313%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farmies-need-their-own-drone-air-force-flown-by-specialists-study-says-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20air%20war%20over%20Ukraine%20has%20become%20a%20cat-and-mouse%20game%20where%20drones%20must%20constantly%20evolve%20to%20survive.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Michael%20Peck)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farmies-need-their-own-drone-air-force-flown-by-specialists-study-says-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Media%20bodies%20flag%20concern%20over%20dire%20state%20of%20'free%20media'%20in%20Pakistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714812681000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109837317%2Cimgsize-18980.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fmedia-bodies-flag-concern-over-dire-state-of-free-media-