33365.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bengaluru%20Woman%20Exposes%20Money-Swiping%20Scam%20Via%20'Bank%20Screenshots'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOnline%20fraud%20is%20increasing%20in%20today's%20world%20where%20digital%20transactions%20have%20become%20the%20norm.%20Scammers%20are%20getting%20smarter.%20They%20use%20clever%20tricks%20to%20deceive%20people%20and%20steal%20their%20money%2C%20like%20sending%20fake%20emails%2C%20setting%20up%20bogus%20websites%2C%20and%20using%20sneaky%20software%20to%20swipe%20your%20sensitive%20info%20like%20credit%20card%20numbers%20and%20passwords.%20Now%2C%20a%20new%20scamming%20trend%20is%20on%20the%20rise%2C%20shared%20by%20a%20Bengaluru%20woman%2C%20named%20Aditi%20Chopra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Chopra%20shared%20an%20incident%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20recounting%20how%20she%20narrowly%20avoided%20falling%20victim%20to%20a%20financial%20scam%20that%20preys%20on%20unsuspecting%20people%20through%20SMS.%20She%20detailed%20how%20she%20was%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20an%20office%20call%20when%20she%20received%20a%20phone%20call%20from%20%E2%80%9Can%20elderly%20sounding%20guy%E2%80%9D%20claiming%20to%20need%20to%20transfer%20money%20to%20her%20father.%20The%20man%20said%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%E2%80%9CAditi%2C%20dear%2C%20I%20needed%20to%20send%20money%20to%20your%20father%20but%20he%20is%20not%20available%2C%20so%20he%20asked%20me%20to%20send%20it%20to%20you.%20Dear%2C%20please%20check%2C%20is%20this%20your%20number%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20cited%20issues%20with%20his%20own%20bank%20account%20and%20requested%20Aditi's%20help%20in%20receiving%20the%20funds.%20Shortly%20after%20the%20call%2C%20Ms%20Chopra%20received%20SMS%20alerts%2C%20which%20seemingly%20showed%20confirmation%20of%20her%20getting%20funds%20into%20her%20account.%20%E2%80%9CI%20first%20received%20an%20SMS%20mentioning%20an%20INR%2010k%20credit%2C%20then%20an%20INR%2030k%20credit%2C%20all%20while%20he's%20on%20the%20call%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20wrote%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caller%20then%20informed%20Ms%20Chopra%20of%20an%20alleged%20mistake%2C%20claiming%20to%20have%20sent%20%E2%82%B930%2C000%20instead%20of%20%E2%82%B93%2C000.%20%26quot%3BDear%2C%20I%20was%20supposed%20to%20send%20only%20INR%203%2C000%2C%20but%20mistakenly%20sent%20INR%2030%2C000.%20Please%20return%20the%20extra%20money.%20I%20am%20standing%20at%20the%20doctor's%20place%2C%20I%20need%20to%20give%20him%20the%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20allegedly%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20close%20inspection%2C%20Ms%20Chopra%20noticed%20that%20the%20SMS%20alerts%20did%20not%20come%20from%20a%20legitimate%20bank%2C%20but%20rather%20from%20a%2010-digit%20phone%20number.%20She%20recognised%20the%20red%20flags%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9COf%20course%20when%20I%20called%20back%20in%20a%20minute's%20time%20after%20checking%20my%20accounts%2C%20I%20was%20blocked.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20further%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20could%20falter%20and%20give%20in%20but%20(I%20know)%20my%20dad%2C%20he%20over%20explains%20everything%20and%20triple%20checks%20in%20matters%20of%20money%2C%20whatever%20be%20the%20amount%2C%E2%80%9D%20claiming%20%E2%80%9Che%20would%20have%20called%20beforehand%20and%20given%20me%20more%20context%20than%20needed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20post%20here%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAnother%20day%2C%20another%20financial%20fraud%20scheme%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnTLDR%3A%20Please%20read%20and%20make%20sure%20you%20don't%20trust%20any%20SMSes%20regarding%20financial%20transactions.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIncident%3A%20Was%20busy%20on%20an%20office%20call%20when%20this%20elderly%20sounding%20guy%20calls%20me%20and%20says%2C%20%E2%80%98Aditi%20beta%2C%20papa%20ko%20paise%20bhejne%20the%20par%20unko%20ja%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A